1563,"uid":296923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:22:55.000Z","msg":"我地draft定問題答案!"},{"pid":"7d4d45203e7eb9d3ba3b52051bc5ffe9908c6c7b","tid":1411563,"uid":282415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:48:14.000Z","msg":"連登仔女好叻叻，一日時間就組織到個Press Con，仲有埋正式invitation<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見三位代表答得有文有路，答Q都有技巧又言之有物，好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n介唔介意我對技術上，有少少提議：<br />\n- 記者收音係用自己咪，如果場地唔大，可以考慮唔需要用場地咪，否則出尼條聲會唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 反而記者提問最好有咪，聽live有D太細聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 如果要咬耳仔討論點答問題，小心記者咪會收到音，最好離遠D，唔係就入晒咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後，香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：傳媒界逃兵"},{"pid":"df5c73798ceaf43fbda2646c977242f021cb52f8","tid":1411563,"uid":281744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:24:09.000Z","msg":"有朋友提議：<br />\n其實，代表性條party line，可以係：「連登係一個開放平台，我地代表有份關注我地平台嘅各界朋友，亦歡迎大家提出意見俾我地改善。<br />\n<br />\n同時，此記者會係補充資訊俾不能接觸連登嘅朋友，讓大家可以全面了解，才自行定論。<br />\n<br />\n香港可貴嘅地方係可以自由表達意見（起碼目前尚可），希望可以解答到記者嘅提問。」"},{"pid":"1c0dbfffd806e70dc7520047c61df4a5f5b45704","tid":1411563,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:28:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 第一次開算唔錯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 建議每次揾唔同人講，最好有埋唔同年紀<br />\n<br />\n3. 每次同recap何君繞條仆街同黑社會勾結(元朗&amp;荃灣恐襲)<br />\n<br />\n4. 每次都開名&amp;相片展示違規黑警<br />\n<br />\n5. 建議可以比QR code比記者入去相關黑社會黑警post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6. 一定要重新5大訴求</span></span>"},{"pid":"f0eeade2a28c8f34f92d444142123a6067839323","tid":1411563,"uid":281744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:29:38.000Z","msg":"另外，朋友們（一班廢中）想幫忙以後提供公關專業意見，如可以參與，請&ldquo;民主記者會&rdquo;有關朋友聯絡。。。。 <br />\n利申：有超過20年公關經驗的幾個廢中"},{"pid":"2cafe3fffe80357e668928ac1d5131d880c23fce","tid":1411563,"uid":16057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:30:31.000Z","msg":"針對藍絲資訊作出澄清？"}]}